733
00:50:09.718 --> 00:50:10.718
Bud?

734
00:50:10.719 --> 00:50:11.803
Zack?

735
00:50:13.055 --> 00:50:14.056
Zack. are you okay?

736
00:50:18.560 --> 00:50:19.561
Zack?

737
00:50:20.479 --> 00:50:22.022
It's okay. It's okay.

738
00:50:22.648 --> 00:50:23.814
